doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width')
    title= title
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge')
    meta(name='description', content='')
    meta(name='keywords', content='')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no')
    title BLOG index with sidebar & slider  | Amaze UI Examples
    meta(name='renderer', content='webkit')
    meta(http-equiv='Cache-Control', content='no-siteapp')
    link(rel='icon', type='image/png', href='/blog/assets/i/favicon.png')
    meta(name='mobile-web-app-capable', content='yes')
    link(rel='icon', sizes='192x192', href='/blog/assets/i/app-icon72x72@2x.png')
    meta(name='apple-mobile-web-app-capable', content='yes')
    meta(name='apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style', content='black')
    meta(name='apple-mobile-web-app-title', content='Amaze UI')
    link(rel='apple-touch-icon-precomposed', href='/blog/assets/i/app-icon72x72@2x.png')
    meta(name='msapplication-TileImage', content='/blog/assets/i/app-icon72x72@2x.png')
    meta(name='msapplication-TileColor', content='#0e90d2')
    block css
      link(rel='stylesheet', href='/blog/assets/css/amazeui.min.css')
      link(rel='stylesheet', href='/blog/assets/css/app.css')
    block js
      if ENV_DEVELOPMENT
        script(src='http://localhost:35729/livereload.js')
    block header
      body#blog
        header.am-g.am-g-fixed.blog-fixed.blog-text-center.blog-header
            .am-u-sm-8.am-u-sm-centered
                img(width='200', src='http://s.amazeui.org/media/i/brand/amazeui-b.png', alt='Amaze UI Logo')
                h2.am-hide-sm-only 中国首个开源 HTML5 跨屏前端框架
        hr
        // nav start
        nav.am-g.am-g-fixed.blog-fixed.blog-nav
            button.am-topbar-btn.am-topbar-toggle.am-btn.am-btn-sm.am-btn-success.am-show-sm-only.blog-button(data-am-collapse="{target: '#blog-collapse'}")
                span.am-sr-only 导航切换
                span.am-icon-bars
            #blog-collapse.am-collapse.am-topbar-collapse
                ul.am-nav.am-nav-pills.am-topbar-nav
                    li.am-active
                        a(href='lw-index.html') 首页
                    li.am-dropdown(data-am-dropdown='')
                        a.am-dropdown-toggle(data-am-dropdown-toggle='', href='javascript:;')
                            | 首页布局 
                            span.am-icon-caret-down
                        ul.am-dropdown-content
                            li
                                a(href='lw-index.html') 1. blog-index-standard
                            li
                                a(href='lw-index-nosidebar.html') 2. blog-index-nosidebar
                            li
                                a(href='lw-index-center.html') 3. blog-index-layout
                            li
                                a(href='lw-index-noslider.html') 4. blog-index-noslider
                    li
                        a(href='lw-article.html') 标准文章
                    li
                        a(href='lw-img.html') 图片库
                    li
                        a(href='lw-article-fullwidth.html') 全宽页面
                    li
                        a(href='lw-timeline.html') 存档
                form.am-topbar-form.am-topbar-right.am-form-inline(role='search')
                    .am-form-group
                        input.am-form-field.am-input-sm(type='text', placeholder='搜索')
        hr
    block content
    block footer
        footer.blog-footer
                .am-g.am-g-fixed.blog-fixed.am-u-sm-centered.blog-footer-padding
                    .am-u-sm-12.am-u-md-4-.am-u-lg-4
                        h3 模板简介
                        p.am-text-sm
                            | 这是一个使用amazeUI做的简单的前端模板。
                            br
                            |  博客/ 资讯类 前端模板 
                            br
                            |  支持响应式，多种布局，包括主页、文章页、媒体页、分类页等
                            br
                            | 嗯嗯嗯，不知道说啥了。外面的世界真精彩
                            br
                            br
                            |             Amaze UI 使用 MIT 许可证发布，用户可以自由使用、复制、修改、合并、出版发行、散布、再授权及贩售 Amaze UI 及其副本。
                    .am-u-sm-12.am-u-md-4-.am-u-lg-4
                        h3 社交账号
                        p
                            a(href='')
                                span.am-icon-qq.am-icon-fw.am-primary.blog-icon.blog-icon
                            a(href='')
                                span.am-icon-github.am-icon-fw.blog-icon.blog-icon
                            a(href='')
                                span.am-icon-weibo.am-icon-fw.blog-icon.blog-icon
                            a(href='')
                                span.am-icon-reddit.am-icon-fw.blog-icon.blog-icon
                            a(href='')
                                span.am-icon-weixin.am-icon-fw.blog-icon.blog-icon
                        h3 Credits
                        p 我们追求卓越，然时间、经验、能力有限。Amaze UI 有很多不足的地方，希望大家包容、不吝赐教，给我们提意见、建议。感谢你们！
                    .am-u-sm-12.am-u-md-4-.am-u-lg-4
                        h1 我们站在巨人的肩膀上
                        h3 Heroes
                        p
                            ul
                                li jQuery
                                li Zepto.js
                                li Seajs
                                li LESS
                                li ...
